16 (a) Upon approval by the transportation commission,
17 the planning, design and construction of the following
18 projects shall be authorized for the funds made available
19 under W.S. 9-1-420:
20
21 (i) The creation of passing lanes, where
22 appropriate, on the portion of United States highway 20
23 between Casper, Wyoming and Waltman, Wyoming;
