6 (iii) The creation of passing lanes, where
7 appropriate, on the portion of the United States highway 20
8 between Shoshoni, Wyoming and Thermopolis, Wyoming;
9
10 (iv) The portion of United States highway 287
11 between Laramie, Wyoming and the Colorado state line that
12 consists of only two (2) lanes in order to make that
13 portion of the highway four (4) lanes;
