1 of the task force under this subsection if they are not
2 reimbursed by their employer. Task force members who are
3 not state employees shall receive per diem and mileage in
4 the amount provided for members of the legislature under
5 W.S. 28-5-101.
6
7 (e) The task force shall terminate December 31, 2026.
